The open kitchen includes a highly functional separate prep kitchen & pantry area with additional appliances, extensive storage & counter space and walk in pantry ideal for a family & active cook. The master suite has a vaulted ceiling with linear fireplace with an ensuite bath featuring soaking tub, large walk in shower & dual closets. Downstairs has another 3 bedrooms with en suite baths and 2 large game rooms. One game room houses a wet bar with barstool seating & the other is currently a convertible media room with sliding doors that open to the huge backyard. (The 6th bedroom is currently being used as a fitness studio with fitness flooring). The U shaped layout surrounds the Watercrest built saltwater pool & spa with water features & firebowls creating privacy, easy access to the outdoor patio & great entertaining space! The large travertine surface patio includes screened covered areas with fireplace, built in grill & smoker as well as open patio with gas firepit & leisure seating with extensive landscape lighting & sound system. Unique features include entire home Generac generator, motorized attic ladder, 5 car garage, motorized shades, custom recessed television cabinets in office & casual dining room, custom shelving throughout, safe room with concrete walls and more.
